וסף גינזבורג\">חיים יוסף גינזבורג</a><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/index.php/%D7%AA%D7%91%D7%A0%D7%99%D7%AA:%D7%95%D7%99%D7%93%D7%90%D7%95\" title=\"קובץ וידאו\"><img alt=\"קובץ וידאו\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/46/%D7%95%D7%99%D7%93%D7%90%D7%95.png/16px-%D7%95%D7%99%D7%93%D7%90%D7%95.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/46/%D7%95%D7%99%D7%93%D7%90%D7%95.png/24px-%D7%95%D7%99%D7%93%D7%90%D7%95.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/46/%D7%95%D7%99%D7%93%D7%90%D7%95.png/32px-%D7%95%D7%99%D7%93%D7%90%D7%95.png 2x\" /></a></span> <span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/index.php/%D7%97%D7%91%22%D7%93_%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95\" title=\"קישור לאתר חב&quot;ד אינפו\"><img alt=\"קישור לאתר חב&quot;ד אינפו\" src=\"/images/thumb/e/ec/%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg/29px-%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"29\" height=\"9\" class=\"mw-file-element\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/e/ec/%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg/44px-%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/e/ec/%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg/58px-%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%A4%D7%95.jpg 2x\" /></a></span></li></ul>\n<table class=\"navbox nowraplinks\" style=\"width: 95%; clear: both; margin: 0.5em auto; margin-top: 0.5em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; padding: 0.2em; text-align: right;\">\n\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"3\" style=\"text-align: center; padding-top: 0.1em; padding-bottom: 0.1em; color: black; background:#8B0000; font-weight: bold;\"><a href=\"/index.php/%D7%93%D7%91%D7%A8_%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%9B%D7%95%D7%AA\" title=\"דבר מלכות\"><span style=\"color:white;\"><b>שיחות הדבר מלכות</b></span></a>\n</th></tr>\n\n\n\n<tr>\n<td style=\"background-color: #8B0000; text-align: right; font-weight: bold; padding-left: 5px;\"><div style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"color:white;\"><b>בראשית</b></span></div>\n</td>\n<td style=\"padding-right: 5px; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"/index.php/%D7%93%D7%91%D7%A8_%D7%9E%D7%9C%D7%9B%D7%95%D7%A